This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with visual perception models and image classification and object detection tasks. It is also likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-category as it discusses transfer learning and pretraining of large convolutional networks. Additionally, it may belong to the Computation and Language (cs.CL) sub-category as it mentions predicting hashtags on social media images. Multimedia (cs.MM) and Information Retrieval (cs.IR) are also possible sub-categories as they deal with large-scale datasets and empirical data analysis, which are relevant to this paper.
